---
title: Brown Sugar Crusted Pork Chops with Butternut Squash
description: Sticky, crispy and oh-so good! Brown sugar-glazed pork chops are the perfect winter pairing for roasted squash and savoury green beans. The grainy mustard aioli is the obvious dipper pairing for these premium chops.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cotelette-de-porc-en-croute-de-cassonade-42497912.jpg
